{"tid":1309374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"莊文龍指保險公司改稱可處理個案 見到配有胡椒噴霧的警察會感到驚慌","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T07:47:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2211bdaed9306f4b08dc7a616e68913ec504318","tid":1309374,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"香港電台外判司機莊文龍在612金鐘衝突事件當日，負責運送器材予採訪隊，懷疑因催淚彈受傷，事隔一個月，多處皮膚敏感發炎，腹部及腳部等生瘡，亦有水泡，需要放膿。<br />\n<br />\n莊文龍憶述，當日在現場下車時，見到車胎中彈，其中有子彈在他的腳旁爆開，爆出白色粉末，他打算逃走，但隨即暈倒。他說，有看過皮膚科及耳鼻喉科醫生，並引述醫生指，可能因為催淚氣體殘餘在皮膚上，導致敏感及發炎。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，經常皮膚痕癢，並懷疑聽力受損，他引述醫生指耳道有點發紅，建議他接受聽力測試，再決定是否需要檢視耳內有否生瘡。<br />\n<br />\n莊文龍說，保險公司最初因為當局稱有關事件為「暴動」，不作賠償，但近日又指，可再處理他的個案。他說，明日會與律師商討如何跟進。他又說，事發後不想再多看衝突畫面，當見到配有胡椒噴霧的警察，會感到驚慌，經常感到疲累。"},{"pid":"0cf6b666328f03ab4d7bb4aab41355834c24394c","tid":1309374,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467994-20190712.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467994-20190712.htm&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=83cff471\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467994-20190712.htm&h=de359dc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467994-20190712.htm</a>"},{"pid":"788d0a15b43b50494e545a3160fc43cf9a3951b7","tid":1309374,"uid":215876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"向警務處索償"},{"pid":"a3c0b3fb34e1c8bbcb22a6cb82f751091a6a305f","tid":1309374,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938a032e9867100dfbf8d04144f950e8e9d834fe","tid":1309374,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"788d0a15b43b50494e545a3160fc43cf9a3951b7","tid":1309374,"uid":215876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"向警務處索償"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"應該要民事索償<br />\n明明唔關事既人俾人槍撃"},{"pid":"0befb7ffbb8701dc2a4da59c1942010345bc137a","tid":1309374,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"邊間保險公司？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef7e0513c9919abda313b4d711d6affa0aaf36c","tid":1309374,"uid":202511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"記者唔使開工了"}]}